  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Empower and protect Dalit girls during lockdown</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">COVID-19 is having a major impact on the lives of Dalit girls in Bangladesh. Schools are closed, families are poorer and girls are isolated from protection services. They are missing out on their education, don&apos;t have access to hygiene products and, hidden behind closed doors, are victims of violence and child marriage. We teach girls to produce their own face masks and sanitary pads and empower them to go back to school. Together we make girls visible and safe again.</narrative>
  </description>
